title: Did NYT Report Clinton and Soros ‘Paid Woman to Accuse Trump of Sexual Assault’?
subtitle: A right-leaning website grossly misrepresented what a two-year-old New York Times article actually said.
author: Dan MacGuill
vclaim: The New York Times stated, as fact, that Hillary Clinton and George Soros had been responsible for paying a woman to make false allegations of sexual assault against Donald Trump.
